description: Gourmet Hot Dogs started in 2005 selling Hot Dogs near Comerica Park. In 2008 Gourmet Hot Dogs decided to go commercial and opened a restaurant booth located on John R and Woodward. At the John R location, Gourmet Hot Dogs became know for the Cleveland Style Polish Boy, Detroit Dog of Champions, and the Big Red Hot. These hot dog sensations named Gourmet Hot Dogs the best hot dog stand in 2011 from Metro Times. Today Gourmet Hot Dogs has taking their famous Hot dogs on the road by starting a mobile Food Service.
name: Gourmet Hot Dogs Detroit
